#: ../../content/administration.rst:8
msgid "Database management"
msgstr "Administration af database"

#: ../../content/administration.rst:10
msgid ""
"These guides provide instructions on how to install, maintain and upgrade "
"Odoo databases."
msgstr ""
"Disse vejledninger giver instruktioner om, hvordan man installerer, "
"vedligeholder og opgraderer Odoo-databaser."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`History of Versions <administration/standard_extended_support>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Versionshistorik <administration/standard_extended_support>`"

#: ../../content/administration.rst:16
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/geo_ip.rst:9
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Installation"

#: ../../content/administration.rst:18
msgid ""
"Depending on the intended use case, there are multiple ways to install Odoo "
"- or not install it at all."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af det tilsigtede anvendelsesformål er der flere måder at "
"installere Odoo på - eller slet ikke installere det."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:21
msgid ""
":doc:`Online <administration/odoo_online>` is the easiest way to use Odoo in "
"production or to try it."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Online <administration/odoo_online>` er den nemmeste måde at bruge "
"Odoo i produktion eller til at prøve det."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:23
msgid ""
":doc:`Packaged installers <administration/on_premise/packages>` are suitable "
"for testing Odoo and developing modules. They can be used for long-term "
"production with additional deployment and maintenance work."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pakkede installationsprogrammer <administration/on_premise/packages>` "
"er egnede til at teste Odoo og udvikle moduler. De kan bruges til langsigtet "
"produktion med yderligere implementerings- og vedligeholdelsesarbejde."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:27
msgid ""
":doc:`Source install <administration/on_premise/source>` provides greater "
"flexibility, as it allows, for example, running multiple Odoo versions on "
"the same system. It is adequate to develop modules and can be used as a base "
"for production deployment."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kildeinstallation <administration/on_premise/source>` giver større "
"fleksibilitet, da det f.eks. muliggør kørsel af flere Odoo-versioner på "
"samme system. Det er egnet til at udvikle moduler og kan bruges som basis "
"for produktionsimplementering."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:31
msgid ""
"A `Docker <https://hub.docker.com/_/odoo/>`_ base image is available for "
"development or deployment."
msgstr ""
"Et `Docker <https://hub.docker.com/_/odoo/>`_ basisimage er tilgængeligt til "
"udvikling eller implementering."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:37
msgid "Editions"
msgstr "Udgaver"

#: ../../content/administration.rst:39
msgid "There are two different editions."
msgstr "Der er to forskellige udgaver."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:41
msgid ""
"**Odoo Community** is the free and open-source version of the software, "
"licensed under the `GNU LGPLv3 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/master/"
"LICENSE>`_. It is the core upon which Odoo Enterprise is built."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Community** er den gratis og open source-version af softwaren, "
"licenseret under `GNU LGPLv3 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/master/"
"LICENSE>`_. Det er kernen, som Odoo Enterprise er bygget på."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:45
msgid ""
"**Odoo Enterprise** is the shared source version of the software, giving "
"access to more functionalities, including functional support, upgrades, and "
"hosting. `Pricing <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ starts from one app "
"free."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Enterprise** er den delte kilde-version af softwaren, der giver "
"adgang til flere funktionaliteter, herunder funktionel support, "
"opgraderinger og hosting. `Priser <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ "
"starter fra én gratis app."

#: ../../content/administration.rst:50
msgid ""
":doc:`Switch from Community to Enterprise <administration/on_premise/"
"community_to_enterprise>` at any time (except for the source install)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Skift fra Community til Enterprise <administration/on_premise/"
"community_to_enterprise>` når som helst (undtagen ved kildeinstallation)."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:3
msgid "Hosting"
msgstr "Hosting"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:8
msgid "Change hosting solution"
msgstr "Skift hosting-løsning"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:10
msgid ""
"The instructions to change the hosting type of a database depend on the "
"current solution used and to which solution the database should be moved."
msgstr ""
"Instruktionerne til at ændre hosting-typen for en databaseafhænger af den "
"nuværende løsning, der bruges, og til hvilken løsning databasen skal flyttes."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:14
msgid "Transferring an on-premise database"
msgstr "Overførsel af en on-premise database"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:17
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:106
msgid "To Odoo Online"
msgstr "Til Odoo Online"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:20
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:109
msgid "Odoo Online is *not* compatible with **non-standard apps**."
msgstr "Odoo Online er *ikke* kompatibel med **ikke-standardapps**."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:21
msgid ""
"The database's current version must be :doc:`supported "
"<standard_extended_support>`."
msgstr ""
"Databasens nuværende version skal være :doc:`understøttet "
"<standard_extended_support>`."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:23
msgid "Create a :ref:`duplicate of the database <on-premise/duplicate>`."
msgstr "Opret en :ref:`duplikat af databasen <on-premise/duplicate>`."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:24
msgid "In this duplicate, uninstall all **non-standard apps**."
msgstr "I denne duplikat skal du afinstallere alle **ikke-standardapps**."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:25
msgid "Use the database manager to grab a *dump with filestore*."
msgstr "Brug databaseadministratoren til at hente en *dump med filestore*."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:26
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:112
msgid ""
"`Create a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/help-form>`_ including the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Opret en `supportbillet <https://www.odoo.com/help-form>`_, der inkluderer "
"følgende:"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:28
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:114
msgid "your **subscription number**,"
msgstr "dit **abonnementsnummer**,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:29
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:115
msgid ""
"the **URL** you want to use for the database (e.g., `company.odoo.com`),"
msgstr ""
"den **URL**, du ønsker at bruge til databasen (f.eks. `company.odoo.com`),"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:30
msgid ""
"the **dump** as an attachment or as a link to the file (required for 60 MB+ "
"files),"
msgstr ""
"**výpis** jako přílohu nebo jako odkaz na soubor (požadováno pro soubory o "
"velikosti 60 MB a více),"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:31
msgid "the **region** you wish to be hosted in,"
msgstr "**region**, ve kterém si přejete být hostováni,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:34
msgid ""
"The list of available regions is available in `our privacy policy <https://"
"www.odoo.com/privacy#data-transfer>`_."
msgstr ""
"Seznam dostupných regionů je k dispozici v `našich zásadách ochrany osobních "
"údajů <https://www.odoo.com/privacy#data-transfer>`_."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:36
msgid "the **name** you want for the database,"
msgstr "**název**, který chcete pro databázi,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:37
msgid "what **version** the database is in,"
msgstr "jaká **verze** databáze je,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:38
msgid "the login (email) of the **administrator** user,"
msgstr "přihlašovací jméno (e-mail) uživatele **správce**,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:39
msgid "whether you wish to have a first **test** deployment, and"
msgstr "zda si přejete prvotní **testovací** nasazení, a"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:42
msgid ""
"This is strongly recommended, especially if you have ever installed third-"
"party apps."
msgstr ""
"Dette anbefales stærkt, især hvis du nogensinde har installeret "
"tredjepartsapps."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:44
msgid ""
"**when** you will want the production database to be put online (day, time "
"of day, and your timezone)."
msgstr ""
"**hvornår** du ønsker, at produktionsdatabasen skal sættes online (dag, "
"tidspunkt på dagen og din tidszone)."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:46
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:121
msgid ""
"Odoo then makes sure the database is compatible before putting it online. In "
"case of technical issues during the process, Odoo might contact you."
msgstr ""
"Odoo sørger derefter for, at databasen er kompatibel, før den sættes online. "
"I tilfælde af tekniske problemer under processen kan Odoo kontakte dig."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:50
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:125
msgid ""
"If you have time constraints, `create a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help-form>`_ as soon as possible to schedule the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har tidsbegrænsninger, `opret en support-ticket <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help-form>`_ så hurtigt som muligt for at planlægge overførslen."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:54
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:92
msgid "To Odoo.sh"
msgstr "Til Odoo.sh"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:56
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:99
msgid ""
"Follow the instructions found in :ref:`the Import a database section <odoo-"
"sh/create/import>` of the Odoo.sh *Create a project* documentation."
msgstr ""
"Følg instruktionerne i :ref:`afsnittet Importér en database <odoo-sh/create/"
"import>` i Odoo.sh-dokumentationen *Opret et projekt*."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:60
msgid "Transferring an Odoo Online database"
msgstr "Overførsel af en Odoo Online-database"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:63
msgid ""
"Odoo Online's :doc:`intermediary versions <standard_extended_support>` are "
"not supported by Odoo.sh or on-premise. Therefore, if the database to "
"transfer is running an intermediary version, it must be upgraded first to "
"the next :doc:`major version <standard_extended_support>`, waiting for its "
"release if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Onlines :doc:`mellemversioner <standard_extended_support>` understøttes "
"ikke af Odoo.sh eller on-premise. Hvis databasen, der skal overføres, kører "
"en mellemversion, skal den derfor først opgraderes til den næste "
":doc:`hovedversion <standard_extended_support>`, om nødvendigt ved at vente "
"på dens udgivelse."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:69
msgid ""
"Transferring an online database running on Odoo 16.3 would require first "
"upgrading it to Odoo 17.0."
msgstr ""
"Overførsel af en online-database, der kører på Odoo 16.3, vil kræve, at den "
"først opgraderes til Odoo 17.0."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:73
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database "
"name on the `Odoo Online database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases/"
">`_ to display its version number."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`tandhjul`)-knappen ved siden af "
"databasenavnet i `Odoo Online database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/"
"databases/>`_ for at vise dens versionsnummer."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:77
msgid ""
"If there is an active Odoo subscription linked to the database being "
"migrated, reach out to the Customer Service Manager or `contact Odoo support "
"<https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ to complete the subscription transfer."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er et aktivt Odoo-abonnement knyttet til den database, der "
"migreres, skal du kontakte Customer Service Manager eller `kontakte Odoo "
"support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ for at gennemføre "
"abonnementsoverførslen."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:82
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:134
msgid "To on-premise"
msgstr "Til on-premise"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:84
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:94
msgid ""
"Download a database backup by signing in to `the Odoo Online database "
"manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases/>`_, clicking the :icon:`fa-gear` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database name, then "
"selecting :icon:`fa-cloud-download` :guilabel:`Download`. If the download "
"fails due to the file being too large, `contact Odoo support <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help>`_."
msgstr ""
"Download en database-backup ved at logge ind på `Odoo Online database "
"manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases/>`_, klikke på :icon:`fa-gear` "
"(:guilabel:`tandhjul`)-knappen ved siden af databasenavnet og derefter vælge "
":icon:`fa-cloud-download` :guilabel:`Download`. Hvis downloaden mislykkes, "
"fordi filen er for stor, `kontakt Odoo support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:89
#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:137
msgid ""
"Restore the database from the database manager on your local server using "
"the backup."
msgstr ""
"Gendan databasen fra database manageren på din lokale server ved hjælp af "
"backuppen."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:103
msgid "Transferring an Odoo.sh database"
msgstr "Overførsel af en Odoo.sh-database"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:111
msgid ""
"Uninstall all **non-standard apps** in a staging build before doing it in "
"the production build."
msgstr ""
"Afinstaller alle **ikke-standardapps** i et staging-build, før du gør det i "
"produktions-buildet."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:116
msgid "which **branch** should be migrated,"
msgstr "hvilken **branch** der skal migreres,"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:117
msgid ""
"in which **region** you want the database to be hosted (Americas, Europe, or "
"Asia),"
msgstr ""
"i hvilken **region** du ønsker, at databasen skal hostes (Amerika, Europa "
"eller Asien),"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:118
msgid "which user(s) will be the **administrator(s)**, and"
msgstr "hvilke brugere der skal være **administratorer**, og"

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:119
msgid ""
"**when** (and in which timezone) you want the database to be up and running."
msgstr ""
"**hvornår** (og i hvilken tidszone) du ønsker, at databasen skal være oppe "
"at køre."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:127
msgid "Select the **region** closest to most of your users to reduce latency."
msgstr ""
"Vælg den **region**, der er tættest på de fleste af dine brugere, for at "
"reducere latenstid."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:128
msgid "Future **administrator(s)** must have an Odoo.com account."
msgstr "Fremtidige **administrator(er)** skal have en Odoo.com-konto."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:129
msgid ""
"The **date and time** you want the database to be up and running are helpful "
"to organize the switch from the Odoo.sh server to the Odoo Online servers."
msgstr ""
"**Dato og tidspunkt**, hvor du ønsker, at databasen skal være oppe at køre, "
"er nyttigt for at organisere skiftet fra Odoo.sh-serveren til Odoo Online-"
"serverne."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:131
msgid "Databases are **not reachable** during their migration."
msgstr "Databaser er **ikke tilgængelige** under deres migrering."

#: ../../content/administration/hosting.rst:136
msgid ""
"Download a :ref:`backup of your Odoo.sh production database <odoo-sh/"
"branches/tabs/backups>`."
msgstr ""
"Download en :ref:`backup af din Odoo.sh-produktionsdatabase <odoo-sh/"
"branches/tabs/backups>`."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:3
msgid "Odoo mobile apps"
msgstr "Odoo-mobilapps"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:5
msgid ""
"Two kind of Odoo mobile app exist: the progressive web app (PWA) and store "
"apps. Using the PWA is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Der findes to slags Odoo-mobilapps: den progressive web-app (PWA) og store-"
"apps. Det anbefales at bruge PWA'en."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:9
msgid "Progressive web app (PWA)"
msgstr "Progressiv web-app (PWA)"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:11
msgid ""
"PWAs are web-based applications designed to function across different "
"devices and platforms, leveraging web browsers to deliver user experiences "
"similar to native apps."
msgstr ""
"PWA'er er webbaserede applikationer designet til at fungere på tværs af "
"forskellige enheder og platforme, der udnytter webbrowsere til at levere "
"brugeroplevelser svarende til native apps."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:14
msgid "The Odoo PWA features include:"
msgstr "Odoo PWA'ens funktioner omfatter:"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:16
msgid "Quick access by adding the PWA to a device's home screen"
msgstr "Hurtig adgang ved at tilføje PWA'en til en enheds startskærm"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:17
msgid "Seamless and borderless navigation experience"
msgstr "Problemfri og grænseløs navigationsoplevelse"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:18
msgid "Push notifications"
msgstr "Pushmeddelelser"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:19
msgid "SSO authentication"
msgstr "SSO-autentificering"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install the Odoo PWA, launch a browser supporting PWAs, and sign in to an "
"Odoo database. The instructions to install a PWA depend on the platform and "
"browser used."
msgstr ""
"For at installere Odoo PWA'en skal du starte en browser, der understøtter "
"PWA'er, og logge ind på en Odoo-database. Instruktionerne til at installere "
"en PWA afhænger af den anvendte platform og browser."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:26
msgid "Android"
msgstr "Android"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Chrome**: open Chrome's menu (:guilabel:`⋮`), select :guilabel:`Install "
"app`, and tap :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"**Chrome**: åbn Chromes menu (:guilabel:`⋮`), vælg :guilabel:`Installer "
"app`, og tryk på :guilabel:`Installer`."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Firefox**: open Firefox's menu (:guilabel:`⋮`), "
"select :guilabel:`Install`, and either touch and hold the Odoo icon or "
"tap :guilabel:`Add automatically`."
msgstr ""
"**Firefox**: åbn Firefoxs menu (:guilabel:`⋮`), vælg :guilabel:`Installer`, "
"og enten tryk og hold Odoo-ikonet eller tryk på :guilabel:`Tilføj "
"automatisk`."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:34
msgid ""
"The PWA can also be installed with **Samsung Internet**, **Edge**, and "
"**Opera**."
msgstr ""
"PWA'en kan også installeres med **Samsung Internet**, **Edge** og **Opera**."

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:36
msgid "iOS"
msgstr "iOS"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:38
