"`MDN Web Docs: Installing and uninstalling web apps <https://"
"developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps/Guides/"
"Installing>`_"
msgstr ""
"`MDN Web Docs: Installing and uninstalling web apps <https://"
"developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps/Guides/Installing>"
