"**The Enterprise git repository does not contain the full Odoo source "
"code**. It is only a collection of extra add-ons. The main server code is in "
"the Community edition. Running the Enterprise version means running the "
"server from the Community version with the `addons-path` option set to the "
"folder with the Enterprise edition. It is required to clone both the "
"Community and Enterprise repositories to have a working Odoo Enterprise "
"installation."
msgstr ""
"**Enterprise git-repositoriet indeholder ikke den fulde Odoo-kildekode**. "
"Det er kun en samling af ekstra add-ons. Hovedserveren er i Community-"
"udgaven. At køre Enterprise-versionen betyder at køre serveren fra Community-"
"versionen med `addons-path`-indstillingen sat til mappen med Enterprise-"
"udgaven. Det er påkrævet at klone både Community- og Enterprise-"
"repositorierne for at have en fungerende Odoo Enterprise-installation."

